WEBVTT

00:00.320 --> 00:01.688
Previously on "The Catch"...

00:01.690 --> 00:04.618
We're here with LA's Chief of
Detectives, Nicholas Turner.

00:04.620 --> 00:06.022
Alice Vaughan stole my partner.

00:06.024 --> 00:08.023
She didn't have to steal me. I left.

00:08.026 --> 00:09.892
We had a life together, Ben.

00:09.894 --> 00:12.029
We were going to have a future together.

00:12.031 --> 00:13.897
And then you chose her.

00:13.932 --> 00:15.365
You're engaged to a con man?

00:15.367 --> 00:16.232
Mm-hmm.

00:16.234 --> 00:18.868
I guess it makes sense, given Ethan.

00:18.870 --> 00:20.236
Ethan was a mistake.

00:20.238 --> 00:21.771
- Are you happy?
- I am.

00:21.773 --> 00:23.406
That's all I ever wanted.

00:23.408 --> 00:27.010
I think you'd rather destroy
the Firm than let me have it.

00:27.012 --> 00:29.745
I can hardly coordinate
a mutiny from the inside.

00:29.747 --> 00:32.115
Well, if you didn't
do this, then who did?

00:32.116 --> 00:33.783
This is the woman who wants you dead.

00:33.785 --> 00:36.885
She's been studying Margot
Bishop for a long time.

00:36.887 --> 00:38.053
Who are you?

00:38.055 --> 00:41.223
You don't recognize me?
It has been a while.

00:41.225 --> 00:42.224
Mummy.

00:44.000 --> 00:50.074
